 Well, the answer is there's 50 lines out here that we're inheriting from.

26
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,920
 So we'll see some of that.

27
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:45,360
 I'll try to kinda allude to that part where, look, there's magic over there.

28
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:48,200
 And a lot of what you do in Django is use classes and

29
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:52,200
 objects that you didn't even create, meaning that they've got data in them,

