 So we're gonna do this in a very, very simple way.

49
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:05,040
 So we have one template, this cond.html that we've been playing with.

50
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:09,280
 You'll notice it has some HTML and a title and a body tag and some of this.

