00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,680
 We have a class-based view.

70
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,400
 We have a get method in there.

71
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:20,400
 The request data comes in as request.

72
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:25,420
 We told it to parse the slug off the end and pass it to us in the variable guess.

73
00:04:25,420 --> 00:04:28,880
 We make a template, which is exactly what we did before,

